Description:
PERFECT PELION
"One of Clyde's most affordable properties."
Located in the incredibly popular Pasadena Estate, the property at 6 Pelion Avenue is perfectly positioned. Within walking distance to public transport plus very close to the newly established shopping precinct and local schools.
Also within close proximity to the local golf course and Casey Fields means you are a stone's throw from some of the council's premier recreation areas.
The house itself features:
- 3 bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Large, modern kitchen;
- Ducted heating;
- Single car remote garage with internal access;
- Landscaped back yard with appealing courtyard.
